    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >XII Century: Sir Galgano was confined in prison.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After apparition of Saint Michael, he is called upon to eradicating evil that is raging in the soul and human mind subdued by ecclesiastical authority.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Struggle against merciless and bloodthirsty enemies in medieval/dark fantasy environments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sir Galgano is a side-scrolling medieval beat ‘em up game with RPG elements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game places the player in control of the hero.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game drew comparisons to the character The King of Dragons, Rastan Saga, Knights of the Round and Golden Axe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KEY FEATURES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game focuses on the hero, Sir Galgano Guidotti, well-know as Saint Galgano. Player battle the game’s many dangers with weapons and complete quests to acquire experience points, which is used to increase Sir Galgano‘s abilities and purchase equipment. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Progress is made through the game by slashing your way through enemy’s forces in dynamic environments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765250/extras/bd54d0a0bbf6df083f764d44b65dc48e.poster.avif?t=1770157590\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765250/extras/bd54d0a0bbf6df083f764d44b65dc48e.webm?t=1770157590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765250/extras/bd54d0a0bbf6df083f764d44b65dc48e.mp4?t=1770157590\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765250/extras/5647dadd49ec3a0797227bff2c6a0c7b.poster.avif?t=1770157590\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765250/extras/5647dadd49ec3a0797227bff2c6a0c7b.webm?t=1770157590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765250/extras/5647dadd49ec3a0797227bff2c6a0c7b.mp4?t=1770157590\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765250/extras/d682e6e449ab6a487b35c3b8919583f8.poster.avif?t=1770157590\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765250/extras/d682e6e449ab6a487b35c3b8919583f8.webm?t=1770157590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765250/extras/d682e6e449ab6a487b35c3b8919583f8.mp4?t=1770157590\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Parry, roll, dodge and attack. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >He has a variety of weapons, a longsword, a shield and a two-handed sword: there are three modes of attack and many fencing techniques.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765250/extras/940f2f8381d8cb2ff17f151cdfe768e2.poster.avif?t=1770157590\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765250/extras/940f2f8381d8cb2ff17f151cdfe768e2.webm?t=1770157590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765250/extras/940f2f8381d8cb2ff17f151cdfe768e2.mp4?t=1770157590\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765250/extras/3dbd5ef6a0d3a3e1f7123821b1183ce9.poster.avif?t=1770157590\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765250/extras/3dbd5ef6a0d3a3e1f7123821b1183ce9.webm?t=1770157590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765250/extras/3dbd5ef6a0d3a3e1f7123821b1183ce9.mp4?t=1770157590\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765250/extras/5a8c2b5363d3876cc6fa24acf676df86.poster.avif?t=1770157590\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765250/extras/5a8c2b5363d3876cc6fa24acf676df86.webm?t=1770157590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765250/extras/5a8c2b5363d3876cc6fa24acf676df86.mp4?t=1770157590\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Player earn experience points by completing missions. When a player earns enough experience, Sir Galgano’s level increases and the player receives ability points. These points may be used on skill trees and general upgrades have a variety of functions, from raising Sir Galgano’s vitality to improving fencing techniques and activate magic skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765250/extras/a5f8cc30addfc2ceaaa9177da02d6fc9.webp?t=1770157590\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765250/extras/a5f8cc30addfc2ceaaa9177da02d6fc9.poster.avif?t=1770157590\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=338 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765250/extras/7dc70ceec310161eee023af801259c04.poster.avif?t=1770157590\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765250/extras/7dc70ceec310161eee023af801259c04.webm?t=1770157590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765250/extras/7dc70ceec310161eee023af801259c04.mp4?t=1770157590\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
